                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-path-planning-geometric-planning-rapidly-exploring-random-trees-rrt-improving-motion-planning-algorithms-by-efficient-nearest-neighbor-searching-papers-2007-yershova-improving-motion-planning-algorithms-by-md",
