                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-trajectory-planning-kinodynamic-planning-rapidly-exploring-random-trees-rrt-optimal-motion-planning-with-the-half-car-dynamical-model-for-autonomous-high-speed-driving-papers-2013-jeon-optimal-motion-planning-with-the-md",
