                        "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-trajectory-planning-trajectory-generation-minimum-jerk-trajectory-generation-for-differential-wheeled-mobile-robots-papers-2013-palamakumburu-minimum-jerk-trajectory-generation-md",
