                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-trajectory-planning-trajectory-optimization-nonlinear-optimization-using-reachable-sets-for-trajectory-planning-of-automated-vehicles-papers-2021-manzinger-using-reachable-sets-for-trajectory-md",
