                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-trajectory-planning-trajectory-optimization-learning-in-trajectory-optimization-explaining-how-a-deep-neural-network-trained-with-end-to-end-learning-steers-a-car-papers-1704-07911-md",
