                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-trajectory-planning-trajectory-optimization-learning-in-trajectory-optimization-learning-complex-neural-network-policies-with-trajectory-optimization-papers-2014-levine-learning-complex-neural-network-policies-md",
