                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-motion-planning-trajectory-planning-trajectory-optimization-learning-in-trajectory-optimization-learning-aided-warmstart-of-model-predictive-control-in-uncertain-fast-changing-traffic-papers-2310-02918-md",
