                        "id": "content-tree-decision-making-reinforcement-learning-policy-optimization-rl-for-linear-systems-second-order-policy-gradient-methods-for-the-linear-quadratic-regulator-papers-2511-02095-md",
                        "label": "Second-Order Policy Gradient Methods for the Linear Quadratic Regulator",
