                            "id": "content-tree-decision-making-reinforcement-learning-model-based-rl-system-identification-dynamic-mode-decomposition-dmd-accelerating-sampling-based-control-via-learned-linear-koopman-dynamics-papers-2603-05385-md",
                            "label": "Accelerating Sampling-Based Control via Learned Linear Koopman Dynamics",
