                    "id": "content-tree-prediction-motion-prediction-surveys-forecasting-the-past-gradient-based-distribution-shift-detection-in-trajectory-prediction-papers-2604-12425-md",
                    "label": "Forecasting the Past: Gradient-Based Distribution Shift Detection in Trajectory Prediction",
